OL,6,FA murder investigation is underway
OL,7,Fafter a dad was attacked outside a pub
OL,8,Fin Derbyshire.
OL,10,FDavid Thompson, 50, was rushed to
OL,11,Fhospital with serious head injuries
OL,12,Ffollowing an incident near to Ours
OL,13,FBar, in Elmton Road, Creswell, on
OL,14,FSaturday 27 January at around 1.30am.
OL,16,FHe had remained in hospital in a
OL,17,Fcritical condition, but died in the
OL,18,Fearly hours of Wednesday 14 February.
