OL,6,FPaying tribute, his daughter, Emma
OL,7,FThompson said: "Even though Dad was
OL,8,F50, he was full of life and enjoyed
OL,9,Fspending time with his family. He
OL,10,Fwould do anything for anybody.
OL,12,F"We would like to ask for privacy at
OL,13,Fthis time while we grieve for our
OL,14,Floss."
