OL,6,FDetective Inspector Maria Pleace from
OL,7,FDerbyshire Police said: "Our thoughts
OL,8,Fare with the family and friends of Mr
OL,9,FThompson at this difficult time. They
OL,10,Fare being supported by family liaison
OL,11,Fofficers as we continue our
OL,12,Finvestigation into the events which
OL,13,Fled to his death.
OL,15,F"It is vital that we fully understand
OL,16,Fwhat happened that evening and the
OL,17,Ftimeline to an assault which appears
OL,18,Fto have left David with injuries he
OL,19,Fwasn't able to recover from and
OL,20,Ftragically proved fatal."
