OL,6,FDI Pleace added: "I would urge anyone
OL,7,Fwith any information about this
OL,8,Fincident, no matter how small or
OL,9,Ftrivial you think it might be, to get
OL,10,Fin touch with us."
OL,12,FOfficers from Derbyshire Police's
OL,13,Flocal safer neighbourhood policing
OL,14,Fteam are carrying out patrols in the
OL,15,Farea. Anyone in the community with any
OL,16,Fconcerns or information is urged to
OL,17,Fspeak to officers.
